sequenceDiagram
    participant W as Workload
    participant V as Verifier
    participant CA as Credential<br/>Authority
    note over W, CA: Credential Acquisition Phase
    W->>W: Generate Credential Key
    W->>W: Create Credential Request<br/>(incl. Credential Key PoP)
    W->>W: Create Evidence<br/>(incl. Credential Request)
    W->>V: Request Attestation (Evidence)
    V->>V: Appraise Evidence
    V->>V: Compute Credential Attributes
    V->>CA: Request Credential<br/>(Credential Request + Attributes)
    CA->>CA: Create and Sign Credential
    CA->>V: Return Credential
    V->>W: Return Credential<br/>in Attestation Results
